				"synopsis": {
					"type": 23,
					"value": "This is a pure cutscene cinematic dialog. After player activates the main generator in Arcane Tower by placing a Sussur Flower in it, there should be a camera flyover showing how all the tower teleport platforms activate, lights turn on, etc.\r\nThis dialog can be easily triggered from console with\r\n    SetGlobalOsirisFlag UND_ArcaneTower_MainPowerOn"
				}
